@startuml
title MCP Tool Adaptation

participant Agent
participant Tool
participant "MCP Adapter" as MCP
participant "MCP Server" as Server
participant "Enterprise Resource" as Resource

Agent -> Tool: request action
Tool -> MCP: translate to MCP
MCP -> Server: list resources / call tool
Server -> Resource: operate on data
Resource --> Server: result
Server --> MCP: MCP response
MCP --> Tool: normalized response
Tool --> Agent: tool result
@enduml
